                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Reverse a completed transfer. Idempotency is enforced at two layers:\n1. Application layer — locks the transfer row and checks `status = 'reversed'`\n2. Database layer — UNIQUE constraint on `reversal_of`\n\n**Error codes:**\n- `already_reversed` (409) — transfer was already reversed\n- `cannot_reverse` (422) — transfer is failed or is an external deposit/withdrawal\n- `transfer_not_found` (404) — transfer ID not found\n- `insufficient_funds` (422) — destination account has insufficient funds to reverse"
          },
